Interface IScdProperty


  • public interface IScdProperty

    • Property Detail

      • isScan

        A flag indicating if the property is a scan property. When a file is scanned by the RTC source code data scanning process, all scan properties are deleted and then recreated by the scanners associated to the file. Non-scan properties (user added properties) remain unaffected during file scans.
        Returns:

        Sets the flag indicating if the property is a scan property. When a file is scanned by the RTC source code data scanning process, all scan properties are deleted and then recreated by the scanners associated to the file.       • isDuplicate

        boolean isDuplicate(IScdProperty property)
        A property is the duplicate of another property if both the namespace and the name are the same. Values are not compared.
        Parameters:
        property - The property to compare this property with
        Returns:
        true if the namespace and names match
